{
  "chapter": 86,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙以董匡身份赴田单宴会，田单对其风采印象深刻，亲自起身相迎。席间田安以齐国\"顽童\"宝马刁难，项少龙以\"与马同眠\"之法巧妙应对，赢得满座赞叹。赵穆与项少龙密谈，透露田单有意支持其篡位，并已将田贞、田凤赠予田单。项少龙配合赵穆演戏，田单慨然将姊妹花转赠项少龙。晶王后与赵雅均出席宴会，龙阳君对项少龙纠缠不休。话题转向合纵攻秦，姬重主张攻关，田单则分析秦国似强实弱、吕不韦与军方不合，认为应以策略取胜而非强攻。田单对项少龙在秦国的近况了如指掌，指出其弱点是\"过分看重情义\"。宴会后赵雅心事重重欲找项少龙倾诉，项少龙婉拒，携田氏姊妹回府。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_chu",
      "speaker_name": "旦楚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这位当是田相急欲一睹风采的董匡先生了，在下齐人旦楚，乃田相亲卫统军，乘此向先生问好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_chu",
      "speaker_name": "旦楚",
      "listener": "char_pu_bu",
      "text": "蒲兄请把先生交给末将好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "通传武士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "董匡先生到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人说见面不如闻名，我却要说闻名怎如一见，终于得睹董兄风采，幸会之至！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到先生不但养马有心得，剑术亦高明之极，国舅爷曾向我多次提及！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_xia",
      "text": "给董兄在我身旁加个位子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小贞因何如此紧张？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小事小事，美人儿万勿介意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "晶王后",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "别人是喝酒，董先生却是嗅酒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "还不给我退下去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生且随本侯来，我看本侯的衣服也应适合你的身材。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我探听过田单口气，他对孝成王甚具恶感，还暗示若我能登上宝座，定会全力支持。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "齐雨又是什么一回事，怎会把你们的关系泄露给赵雅知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要看赵雅风流浪荡，事实上她比任何人都精明厉害，齐雨只要说错一句话，就会给她抓住尾巴。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷真够本事，竟能弄来如此美艳、容貌身材无不相同的姊妹花，确是难得的尤物。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你何不早说？田单昨晚尝过滋味后赞不绝口，不用他说，我已答应把两女送他，为今怎能反悔？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "却非没有办法，但能否成功，就要看田单对你看重的程度了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生穿起华衣美服，真令人耳目一新。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷说过要带董先生来为人家的马儿看病，为何到现在仍未实践诺言？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "董先生终日往牧场跑，我怎抓得住他呢！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "龙阳君若只是为了马儿，我手下亦有治马的能手，当然及不上董兄，不过也可让低手先出马，看看可否代高手之劳。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_an",
      "speaker_name": "田安",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "敝国有匹名为'顽童'的骏骥，跑起来像一阵风般迅快，可是却无人能把牠驯服，软硬办法均不行，现在有此良机，故要向先生请教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "驯畜之道，首要是让它们对你没有防备之心，但这也只是一般人的下乘手法。上乘之法则是使它们把你视作同类，且是爱护有加，那无论如何野性的马儿，也会变得既听话又合作。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人就是人，畜牲就是畜牲，怎会使畜牲当了人是同类？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "方法多的是，例如畜牲刚出世时首先接触到的任何生物，它们会视之如父母，不信可随便找只初生的鸭子试试看，当知董某不是虚言。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪常有传闻，说弃在荒野的婴儿，有被野狼哺乳养大的，竟变成狼人，正因他以为狼是自己的父母，董先生不愧驯养畜牲的大家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但田大夫所说的'顽童'宝马，却是早已出生，似再没有可能令牠把人视作同类，董先生又有何妙法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鄙人有一驯马之法，万试万灵，一向都是挟技自珍，从没说出来给人知晓，不过今天如此高兴，便让鄙人掏出来向田相献丑吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这方法一听就明，但若非真是爱马的人，却不易做到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是常陪马儿睡觉，那牠就会尽去戒备之心，甚至会视你为同类。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来！让我们为董兄由经验领悟回来的真知灼见喝一杯！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在在下始知先生为何会被冠以'马痴'之名了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田相和董先生不但意气相投，连爱好都没有分别，同为这对越女动心，而董先生得知她们已荣归田相……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "美人归贤主，董某只有恭贺之情，绝无半分妒忌之意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄既有此情，我就把她们双双转赠，让董先生在马儿之外，还另有同眠的伴侣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "由这刻开始，你们两人由田相改赠董爷，务要悉心侍奉，不准有丝毫抗命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "你们立即回去收拾衣物，等待董爷领你们回府吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "晶王后",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有了这对如花似玉的人儿，董先生莫要忘了再和马儿睡觉啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生真的和马儿睡过觉吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "text": "当然，鄙人七岁开始和马儿睡觉，但却非在马厩里，而是在寝室内。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "我也要为君上向董兄说句公道话，那天校场试剑后，纪才女勾勾指头，董兄便立即跟去为她诊马，为何竟对君上却又薄此厚彼？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国舅爷说得对，那天鄙人实不该去的，因纪才女竟和我讨论起礼乐诗文，结果自是教她大为失望，董某亦无颜以对。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_chong",
      "speaker_name": "姬重",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们数次合纵，均攻秦人不下，最主要是因秦人藉地势建立险要的关塞。他们东有函谷关、虎牢关、殽塞，东南则有武关。但只要攻下其中一关，我们便能长驱直进，那时看秦人还有何凭恃？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国家的强大，君权、经济和军力是绝对分不开来的，不过依我看秦国现在是似强实弱，白起死后，秦国军方无人能继，现在庄襄王由吕不韦把持朝政，与军方绝不投合，田某敢担保只要此人一日当权，秦人难以合力齐心，但假若我们现在大举攻秦，则外侮当前，反会逼得秦人合力抵抗，弄巧成拙，各位同意我的看法吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "然则田相是否不同意这次合纵之议呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不是这样，合纵乃势在必行，但手段策略却须仔细商榷，否则本人就不须远道来此了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田相对秦人的动静似是知之甚详，可否告知我们项少龙近况如何，在座很多人都希望听到他惨遭不幸的消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项少龙真不简单，每能以寡胜众，连我的老朋友无忌兄都要阴沟里翻船，给他漂漂亮亮玩了一手，其他的不用我说出来，各位该非常清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田相是否有点长他人志气呢？我看这小贼怕是有点运道吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知彼知己，百战不殆。本人虽恨不得把他碎尸万段，却绝不敢小觑他。项少龙甫到秦境便大展神威，在秦王和文武大臣前力挫秦国第一悍将王翦，以宝刃连挡他铁弓射出来能贯墙穿盾的劲箭。依我看，他还是手下留情，不想秦国军方下不了台。秦王当场赐他太傅之职，吕不韦亦因他声威大振。此子不除，吕不韦就若如虎添翼，终有一日能把持秦政。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_chong",
      "speaker_name": "姬重",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "如此听来，秦人应不会缺乏想置他于死地的人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_ji_chong",
      "text": "项少龙若是如此容易被杀死，他早死过无数次，秦人亦曾对他发动暗袭，却只闹个灰头土脸，还赔上几个人。现在乌家在秦声势日盛，正是拜项少龙所赐，连秦国军方里敌视吕不韦的人，亦对此子另眼相看，希望把他争取过去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "晶王后",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我才不信没有人对付得了他，他又不是三头六臂。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然有对付他的方法，田相……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人都有他的弱点，项少龙的弱点是过分看重情义，心肠太软，这将会成为他的致命伤。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那对美人儿正在马车上等候董先生，趁路上有点时间，先生大可详细验货。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来郭家快要多了个当国舅的娇婿了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本想和董先生作伴乘车，不过董先生另有美人相待，不若奴家明天来探望先生吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "真不好意思，明天我还要到牧场督工，嘿！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那就更好，整天困在城里，不若到外边走走，天亮时奴家来找你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "要不要本侯传你两招，包可收得他服服帖帖。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷有心，却请免矣。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "韩侯请先回去吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夜深了！让鄙人送夫人上车好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    }
  ],
